RES osdtriplet
! Batch 3: tilt and decenter commands with RSI/FIR verification
STILT 2 0.5 0 0
RSI f1 w1 0.0 0.7
RES osdtriplet
BTILT 2 4 0.5 0 0
FIR
RES osdtriplet
! ROLL: start surf must have finite thickness predecessor; use surf 2
ROLL 2 4 0.1 0
RSI f1 w1 0.0 0.7
RES osdtriplet
! DISP: start surf must have finite thickness predecessor; use surf 2
DISP 2 4 0.1 0 0
FIR
RES osdtriplet
PIVAXIS ALL
